{
  "page": "Rognar II Greyiron",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\"><img alt=\"House Greyiron.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/50px-House_Greyiron.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/75px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/100px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Rognar II Greyiron</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\"><img alt=\"House Greyiron.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/50px-House_Greyiron.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/75px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/100px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nRognar Greyiron, Second of His Name Since the <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_King\" title=\"Grey King\">Grey King</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_King\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Iron King\">Iron King</a></li><li>King of the Iron Islands</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harras_Hoare\" title=\"Harras Hoare\">Harras Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Rognar II Greyiron</b> was the last <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rognar_II_Greyiron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rognar II was brought down by <a href=\"/index.php/Pirate\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pirate\">pirates</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellswords</a>, and warlords, <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> who came to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> and allied with <a href=\"/index.php/House_Orkwood\" title=\"House Orkwood\">Orkwoods</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Drumm\" title=\"House Drumm\">Drumms</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">Hoares</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">Greyjoys</a>. He was succeeded by <a href=\"/index.php/Harras_Hoare\" title=\"Harras Hoare\">Harras Hoare</a>, who, according to the tale, won the crown in a contest of the <a href=\"/index.php/Finger_dance\" title=\"Finger dance\">finger dance</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_iron_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_iron_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rognar_II_Greyiron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Urras_Greyiron\" title=\"Urras Greyiron\">Urras<br /><small>Ironfoot</small></a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width: